Courthouse, the pair drove off in his 18-wheeler, which had been
suitably adorned by family and friends.
   ``It's just something different and we wanted to do it,'' said
Windle, a truck driver.
   For their wedding trip, the Fuchses headed for Opryland in
Nashville.
