received permission to be on the flight with the child's father,
Walid Awwad, who was a steward aboard the plane.
   ``Imagine being a steward, working on the flight, and all of a
sudden, your wife is giving birth to your first child,'' Hassett
said.
   Both mother and child were taken to Queens General Hospital in
good condition, he said.
   The child will be a Kuwait citizen, retaining the same
citizenship as his parents, said Hassett, who obtained the
information from immigration officials.
