<HEAD>Woman Gives Birth To Quintuplets</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CLEVELAND (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A woman who had been taking fertility drugs
delivered quintuplets Saturday evening, but one of the infants was
stillborn, a hospital spokeswoman said.
